If a language is not chosen, or if there is no Language column, the cards will default to English.

Foil requires either a blank cell for no foiling, foil for normal foiling, or etched for etched foiling. Special treatments, such as gilded or textured foils, are not accepted and unnecessary. Those cards have their own collector number, which can be used to differentiate them from other treatments.

Collector Number simply requires a number. Rarely, a letter or star (★) will be appended onto the collector numbers of certain cards.

Alter is a boolean field that accepts either TRUE or FALSE. If this field is left blank, Moxfield will assume it is false.

Playtest Card is a boolean field that accepts either TRUE or FALSE. If this field is left blank, Moxfield will assume it is false.

Purchase Price accepts any number rounded to two decimal places. Do not include any currency symbols.

